    "id": "q-ssc-cgl-test-ssc-cgl-full-3211-english-16",
    "text": "P : Unfortunately due to my work schedule and the\nclimbing season wrapping up, it did not come to fruition.\nQ : There was only one problem, I did not have the necessary\nskills for climbing in the snow and ice that is required in the\nhigher elevations, at least if I wanted to be safe and smart.\nR : So for my birthday last year, my wife, bless her heart was\ngoing to buy me a guided trip with beginner snow climbing\nclasses for Mount Hood.\nS : But for my birthday I got my first realization that it was\ngoing to become a reality.\nThe proper sequence should be :",
