    "explanation": "QRPS\nSentence R states that the writer's wife wanted to gift him a\nguided trip to Mount Hood. But Sentence P shows the failure of\nthis plan. So, P will follow R & only option c follows this\nsequence, hence it is the correct answer.",
    "sectionName": "English Comprehension",
    "testId": "test-ssc-cgl-full-3211"
